<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758113>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–2. Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n., unnamed spring tributary to Little River, Montgomery Co., NC. 1. Adult, female. 2. Larva, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758113/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758117>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Distribution of Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758117/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758119>
    dc:description "Figs. 4–6. Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n., adult. 4. Head and pronotum, dorsal, Little Creek, Montgomery, Co., NC. 5. Abdomen, male and female, dorsal, unnamed tributary to Barnes Creek, Montgomery Co., NC. 6. Male sterna 7–10, ventral, Little Creek, Montgomery, Co., NC." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758123>
    dc:description "Figs. 7–9. Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n., adult, unnamed spring tributary to Little River, Montgomery Co., NC. 7–8. Male terminalia, dorsal. 9. Male tergum 9, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758127>
    dc:description "Figs. 10–12. Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n., adult male epiproct, lateral. 10. Unnamed spring tributary to Little River, Montgomery Co., NC (inset: Little Creek, Montgomery, Co., NC). 11–12. Little Creek, Montgomery, Co., NC." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758127/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758129>
    dc:description "Figs. 13–15. Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n., adult, unnamed spring tributary to Little River, Montgomery Co. NC. Fig. 13. Male sub-anal probe, dorsolateral. 14. Female terga 7–10, ventral. 15. Ovum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758129/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758133>
    dc:description "Figs. 16–19. Zealeuctra uwharrie sp. n., larva, unnamed spring tributary to Little River, Montgomery Co. NC. 16. Head, pronotum and thorax, dorsal. 17. Left lacinia, ventral. 18. Left mandible, ventral. 19. Male abdomen, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758133/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758137>
    dc:description "Figs. 20–22. Zealeuctra fraxina, adult, Burden Branch, Pope Co., IL. 20. Male terga 8–10, dorsal. 21. Male terminalia, lateral. 22. Female sterna 7–10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758137/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758139>
    dc:description "Fig. 23. Type locality, unnamed spring tributary to Little River, Montgomery Co., NC, N 35.29628, W 79.88583, 16 January 2019." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758139/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

